The postmaster has received a civic contract for a complete route survey of the Public Dungeons. The dungeon complex is used by a wide range of adventurers and recovery teams, but no current comprehensive map exists in Midgaard's civic archive. Walk every accessible section of the dungeons and return with a complete navigation record so the civic registry can issue standardized reference documents.
Your Public Dungeons survey has been filed with Midgaard's civic archive. The postmaster has forwarded the route record to the public information office, which will incorporate it into the general reference materials available to adventurers registering with the civic registry.

